summary: 3 small bat files to give you a few more points here and there
descriptionHtml:
These are just 3 small bat files that I made for those of us who have to have a bit more a bit earlier.
Just type bat(followed by file name) in the console (press ~ to access) to give yourselves a selection of smithing materials, some flawless gems, and in the main file, a boost to your player stats, 25k gold, 500 lockpicks ,20 filled black soul gems, an ebony sword to disenchant for enchanting (funnily enough) and maybe one or two more things I have forgotten about.
Nothing new, nothing too over-powered, just a few things put together in one place to save having to type in sperately.
author: Userberus
